#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.7/guides/reactive-sql-clients.adoc
msgid "the number of rows affected by the query (inserted/deleted/updated/retrieved depending on the query type),"
msgstr "クエリーの影響を受ける行数 (クエリータイプに応じて挿入/削除/更新/取得)、"

